lazpaint (6.4.1) stable; urgency=low

  * added brush tool and clone tool
  * added palette toolbar
  * docking of toolbox
  * choice of quality when saving PNG/JPG/BMP files
  * rain rendering
  * improved 3d object importation (texture, vertex normals)

